NOTE: Used original README example as template for this README

Accessories:
 * 560 Ohm (Grn Blu Brown) resistor
 * LED
 * Arduino Mega Board (AMG)
 * Potentiometer

Wiring instructions:
Arduino Pin 13 <--> Resistor <--> Longer LED lead |LED| Shorter LED lead <---> Arduino GND
Arduino Analog Pin 0 <--> Potentiometer lead (centre)
AND
Arduino Supply <--> Potentiometer lead (right)
AND
Arduino GND <--> Potentiometer lead (left)

How to run code:
Load into Arduino IDE
Upload from there to said Arduino

Assumptions made:
None

Functionality included that is outside exercise/assignment specification
None

